name: VideoQualityAdaptIndication
description: Quality change of the local video in terms of target frame rate and target bit rate since last count.

parameters.AdaptNone: 0: The local video quality stays the same.

parameters.AdaptUpBandwidth: 1: The local video quality improves because the network bandwidth increases.

parameters.AdaptDownBandwidth: 2: The local video quality deteriorates because the network bandwidth decreases.
